OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FImam Adam Kelwick and dad Mark Scanlon
OL,7,Fspoke to ITV Granada Reports'
OL,8,Fjournalist, Emma Sweeney
OL,10,FAn Imam has hailed the "lightbulb
OL,11,Fmoment" he sat down to find common
OL,12,Fground with a dad who attended a
OL,13,Frecent "Save Our Children" protest.
OL,15,FAdam Kelwick, from the Abdullah
OL,16,FQuilliam Society mosque, in Liverpool
OL,17,F- the oldest mosque in England, was
OL,18,Fcontacted by Mark Scanlon through a
OL,19,Fmutual friend.
