OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FThe pair agreed to meet for a coffee
OL,7,Fwhere they discussed "immigration, the
OL,8,FSouthport tragedy and the psychology
OL,9,Fof hate," explained Mr Kelwick.
OL,11,FImam Adam described the "lightbulb
OL,12,Fmoment" he had when he sat down with
OL,13,FMark Scanlon.
OL,15,F"We had all these amazing discussions
OL,16,Fand right towards the end of the
OL,17,Fdiscussion there was a moment and it
OL,18,Freally was like a lightbulb and it's
OL,19,Flike, people are trying to play us
OL,20,Fagainst each other here, aren't they,"
OL,21,Fhe added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
