OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,F"Everyone realised at the same time
OL,7,Fand it was like, wow."
OL,9,FMr Scanlon said the meeting had helped
OL,10,Fboth men to realise that "we're all
OL,11,Ffacing the same problems... regardless
OL,12,Fof where you come from, what your
OL,13,Fbackground, what your faith is."
OL,15,FThe martial arts specialist explained
OL,16,Fthat he had attended the recent
OL,17,Fprotest as a "concerned parent."
OL,19,FMark Scanlon says the teenagers are
OL,20,F"being manipulated" by social media.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
