OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FHe added: "I felt like it was a space
OL,7,Ffor us to go and, you know, start to
OL,8,Fcome together.
OL,10,F"We know the only way we're going to
OL,11,Fsolve the issues... is by families,
OL,12,Fnormal people just coming together and
OL,13,Ftrying to have their say and be heard."
OL,15,FMr Scanlon said parents everywhere are
OL,16,F"fearful of the future for our kids".
OL,18,F"Teenagers all over the country are
OL,19,Fbeing manipulated", he added, "and
OL,20,Fthey're seeing different things, you
OL,21,Fknow, from social media."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
