OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FThe UK has seen several protests -
OL,7,Fmany of which have seen scenes of
OL,8,Fpublic disorder and violence - after
OL,9,Fthree girls were stabbed to death at a
OL,10,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class in the
OL,11,Ftown.
OL,13,FMr Scanlon said the protest he
OL,14,Fattended on Saturday 3 August had been
OL,15,Fpeaceful - but later in the day, there
OL,16,Fhad been clashes between police and
OL,17,Fother protesters, which spilled onto
OL,18,FThe Strand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
