OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FHe said: "I don't condone the way the
OL,7,Fchildren, the kids, teenagers in our
OL,8,Fcity are behaving now. But for me,
OL,9,Fit's how do we solve it?
OL,11,F"How do we salvage something out of
OL,12,Fthis which makes us stronger
OL,13,Fcollectively as a city."
OL,15,FThe pair are now working together to
OL,16,Fhelp find solutions. They are
OL,17,Fcurrently planning a trip to Wales for
OL,18,Fchildren from all backgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
