OL,3,CImam hails 'lightbulb moment' during
OL,4,Csit-down with protester
OL,6,FMr Kelwick said: "We've received an
OL,7,Finvitation for members of our
OL,8,Fcommunity to join Mark and people from
OL,9,Fhis community and go on the day trip
OL,10,Fto Wales."
OL,12,FChildren will be asked to leave their
OL,13,Fphones to one side and will "literally
OL,14,Fbe forced to walk and talk to each
OL,15,Fother".
